Description: Welcome to the Timbers…This is a unique setting where high quality apartment homes include living in historic Catonsville. Nestled into this environment are three distinctly different, affordable, apartment home developments located on the same campus- Cedar Run, White Oaks, and Shade Tree Trace. Walk to schools, neighborhood shopping, and public transportation plus there is a free shuttle to the University of Maryland, Baltimore Campus. The Timbers is just minutes to downtown Baltimore and an easy commute to Columbia, Annapolis, and the airport. Enjoy living in an established community nestled amidst private homes in a well-maintained neighborhood. Furnished, student and corporate apartments with flexible lease terms are available.

Description:
Charming 1830s 2 bedroom brick home located in Oella. Original heartwood floors, beautiful porch overlook, updated kitchen, across the street from the Patapsco River and state park, walking distance to restaurants and shops in old Ellicott City. Many parks and trails in neighborhood.
Small town feel but very close to Catonsville, Baltimore and Columbia. Easy access to 695, Route 29 and Interstate 70.

Description:
This 2BR house has upgraded kitchen with stacked washer dryer, gas range, gas furnace, fireplaces, and central air conditioning
About a block from the Patapsco River and the beautiful millrace trail, this stone house is less than a ¾ mile walk to the shops and restaurants on Main Street of Old Ellicott City. The Patapsco Valley State Park is to the north and south, and nearby there are hiking/running/biking trails and swimming holes, tubing and kayaking. Many important historic sites are readily accessible. Over 200 years old, this rehabbed duplex is a contributing element to the National Register Historic District of Oella. 
Although a place apart nestled in a river valley, Oella is conveniently located within 10 minutes of Interstate Routes 29 and 695. The Baltimore Inner Harbor, BWI Airport, and Columbia are within 20 minutes. Washington DC is nearby.

Enjoy outdoor living space with a private entrance & a maintenance free lawn. Our open floor plans boast with designer inspired accents. Your new home includes plush wall-to-wall carpet, spacious closets and central air conditioning. Lavish yourself in the comfort you deserve. Lessen your commute and gain back some precious free time. Your new home is only seconds away from Route 40, I-695, I-70, and just minutes from I-95, Route 29, Arundel Mills & Downtown Baltimore. If comfort, convenience and a carefree lifestyle are what you are in search of...your search is over! Welcome Home to Melvin Park!

The spacious kitchen has an abundance of storage and opens to a deck and lower patio area that backs to green space, perfect for entertaining. Large bedrooms with neutral berber carpet and generous closet space share 2 full baths that feature soaking tubs and a double vanity. Shaded yard includes a storage shed and finished basement has a full size washer/dryer! 
Pets welcome with additional deposit!
